        "textHtml": "80-channel C-band WDM, 50 GHz spacing, 100 Gb/s/channel, loss 0.2 dB/km, EDFAs every 80 km. (a) Total capacity. (b) Loss per span and EDFA gain. (c) OSNR after 10 spans. (d) Link viable at 15 dB required OSNR?",
